This script will remove all the DDOS plan in your subscription. 

1.	Check for the VNETs which has DDoS plan associated. 
2.	Disassociates DDoS from all the VNETs in your subscription.
3.	Delete the DDOS plan from your subscription. 

This will be easy and useful as you don’t need to manually navigate to each and every VNETs , disassociating the DDOS plan and deleting it. Moreover, it cost ~ Lakhs/Month.  You can run this script once a week to make sure you don’t have the DDOS plan in your subscription. 

